data.description:
BACK ON MARKET due to unforeseen circumstances of previous buyers.  Inspections are completed and sellers are still MOTIVATED and offering an additional $5k toward repairs!  Current mortgage is assumable with a fantastic interest rate!
Nestled into a 2.5 acre lot with lots of mature trees and wildlife, this 4 bed 3 bath house has so much to offer.  Through the front door you will walk into the open living, dining, and kitchen area.  The kitchen has granite countertops with center island and newer stainless steel appliances along with custom cabinetry.  Off of the kitchen in one direction is a large sunporch with oversized windows and sliding glass door that look to the back of the property making it perfect for watching the deer.  In the other direction you will find the laundry area with custom mud bench and your first full bathroom that features a walk in shower with tile surround and vanity with granite countertop.  Down the hall from the living area are the 3 guest bedrooms and guest bath that has an oversized granite top vanity and shower/bath combo with tile surround.  At the end of the hall, you will find the spacious main bed and main en suite with walk in closet.  The en suite has separate double sinks with granite, a stand alone shower, and separate soaking tub.  The HVAC system was completely overhauled in 2020 that included a huge new a/c unit, heat pump, and all brand new duct work.  All is electric with OEC and has OEC Fiber available.  The exterior of the home includes an approx 20x90 dog run and small animal pens that the owners built for goats and chickens.  There's still plenty of room to expand for what may suit the needs of your family!
